    And I enter attribute in the group file MetaData with the following parameters:
      | componentType  | JVMs          |
      | fileName       | setenv.bat    |
      | group          | seleniumGroup |
      | attributeKey   | "hotDeploy"   |
      | attributeValue | true          |
      | override       | true          |

    When I attempt to deploy the jvm group resource "setenv.bat"
    Then I confirm successful deploy popup
